Package: chatr
Type: Package
Title: An Intelligent, Local Assistant for R Programmers
Version: 0.1.0
Author: ChatR Team
Maintainer: ChatR Team <maintainer@example.com>
Description: ChatR is a lightweight, open, and reliable AI assistant built 
    specifically for R users. It runs locally on your machine without needing 
    a powerful GPU or a proprietary API key. Features include context-aware 
    retrieval, live R code execution, and educational support.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: false
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5.0)
